# DeepDive configuration — copy to `.env` and fill in your own keys.
# NEVER commit the real `.env` — it's gitignored.

# ── Required ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anthropic API key — powers every analysis agent.
# Get one at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Optional: resolution chain tiers ────────────────────────────────────
# Gemini grounded search — one tier of the headline resolution chain and
# a second-opinion fact-checker. Without it, that tier is disabled.
# Get one at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=

# Twitter API v2 bearer token — enables the Twitter reverse-anchor tier
# for breaking-news headline resolution. Without it, that tier is disabled.
# Get one at https://developer.x.com/en/portal/dashboard
TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=

# ── Optional: Google Drive upload ───────────────────────────────────────
# Drops synthesized DOCX reports into a Google Drive folder. Requires
# OAuth credentials at credentials/oauth_client.json (not supported on the
# hosted deployment — use local-only for this feature).

# ── Optional: model overrides ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Defaults are fine; override only if you want to pin a specific model.
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
# CLAUDE_MODEL_HAIKU=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001

# ── Optional: concurrency & storage ─────────────────────────────────────
# MAX_CONCURRENT_AGENTS=4
# VECTOR_DB_PATH=.chromadb
